{"id":"ezrahite","term":"Ezrahite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A title given to Ethan (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 4:31\">1 Kings 4:31</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 89\">Ps. 89</a>, title) and Heman (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 88\">Ps. 88</a>, title). They were both sons of Zerah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:6\">1 Chr. 2:6</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Kings 4:31","Psalms 89","Psalms 88","1 Chronicles 2:6"]}